  1. <Initial Interpretation>

    <program-theory-problem>
      Model <having-a-concept> without treating <concept> as a thing stored inside <mind>.
      Replace the question "What inner item is present?" with: "What can the <actor> now do, recognize, infer, explain, correct, and transfer?"
    </program-theory-problem>

